2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	-  
2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	- RAJANIEMI, Hannu  (1978-). Born in Ylivieska, Finland, Rajaniemi is the
2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	- author of two novels and several short stories, and his debut novel 'The
2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	- Quantum Thief' was nominated for the 2011 Locus Award for Best First
2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	- Novel.  Rajaniemi lives in Edinburgh, Scotland where he is founding
2019-12-17 19:46:20	--	- director of ThinkTank Maths, a commercial research organisation.
